features: 【Give your shoes a neat home】 Are all your shoes stacked in the entryway? USIKEY 8-tier metal shoe rack can fit 31-40 pairs of shoes, enough to meet the use of a family. The wooden countertop at the top is very suitable for those last minute items you need before you head out, such as keys, wallets, umbrellas, etc. Try our shoe rack, your shoes will be happy in their new home.

【Space-saving Shoe Storage Organizer】 Size: 36.2"(L)x11"(W)x53.5"(H), Height between shelves is:7.1", The perfect size greatly extends the vertical space, maintaining a clean and orderly room without occupying too much space. If you have high boots, just remove one of the shelves to create space for them.

【Sturdy and Durable Metal Shoes Rack】The industrial shoe rack is made of thickened metal tube, 7-layer metal shelves, and P2 grade high quality particle board, which ensures the durability and sturdiness for long term use. The metal surface has a waterproof coating, so our shoe rack won't be afraid of wet shoes on rainy days.

【Not just storing shoes!】The simple design and rustic appearance of the shoe storage shelf is sure to make a statement in any room. It can not only be used as a shoe rack, but also as a display rack, plant rack, flower rack, etc. Whether in the living room, bedroom, or corridor, the usikey shoe rack can maximize its function!
【Easy Assembly】Our shoe rack comes with adjustable footpads ,Every part is clearly labeled for easy recognition. You can assemble this free standing shoe racks in 15 minutes.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Tall with lots of shelf space.
reviews.reviewText: This shoe rack was very easy to put together, every piece fit and only took me about 15-20 mins. It is top heavy with the nice wooden top. It comes with straps to secure it to the wall. Great buy!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice and tall with ample space
reviews.reviewText: I like the fact that the top of the shoe organizer has a wood veneer that compliments the black frosted frame. It’s an impressive shoe rack.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Super Easy to Assemble
reviews.reviewText: This shoe rack was super easy to assemble. All of the holes lined up perfectly and I had zero trouble with the process. It has added an extreme amount of space for me to store my shoes and has given me a shelf on top of the rack that I can store other items. I definitely recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy, hold many shoes – but ugly “wood” top.
reviews.reviewText: I like that this shoe rack from usikey holds so many shoes. It is easy to assemble. It is sturdy. The shelfs are even, not slanted like many shoe racks. I can be used for more than shoes. The metal shelves and sides look decent. My issue is with the particle board top. It does look like wood, but they picked an ugly piece of wood to duplicate with the veneer they put on top of the particle board. It looks like an old stained piece of oak. The color isn’t bad, just the grain pattern and blotches. I was thinking “Rustic Brown” meant color. They mean “rustic” as in old & used. Sturdy, hold many shoes – but ugly “wood” top.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fits so many shoes
reviews.reviewText: Easily tips over if not enough wait is added. Other than that it can hold many shoes at once. Keeping shoes organized and easy to choose.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Beware angled bolt holes
reviews.reviewText: Easy to put together but 3 out of the 16 bolt holes for the tier shelves were not tap straight at all as you can see from my pictures. Poor quality tapped so my husband had to re-tap the holes so the bolts don't strip out when screwing them in. Easy fix if you have the right tools and know how but one should honestly not have to do this for a purchased item.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Functional and easy to put together.
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased this shoe rack, is easy to assemble, my son put it together all by himself. It is spacious accommodating many pair of shoes. Furthermore, the top shelves is great, we use it a a book shelf. The material quality is not bad, and the color scheme is pretty nice it match the wall pipe shelf I purchased.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I love this shoe rack
reviews.reviewText: I absolutely love this shoe rack! It is big and holds a ton of my family's shoes! I have it right next to the door, so it is easy for people to take their shoes off at the door and place them on the shoe rack. I love the top portion, as we have small decorations and a bin to place odd items in. We love it and are pleased with this order.
